abalawuli ekwabelwana / iifayile - ezi abalawuli / iifayile kungadingeki ukuba umsebenzisi ungqinisiso *, loo nto ithetha ukuba ziyafumaneka kuzo zonke iindwendwe * (ukuba babe ikhonkco). Qinisekisa ukuba i-akhawunti umsebenzisi abangaziwayo yabelwe abangamavolontiya \ Anonymousdownload.ashx uye NTFS iimvume zokufunda / ukubhala ezineenkcukacha / ifayile
